data.text:
Product Description

Title : Barry Gibb & Friends – Greenfields. Format : Vinyl Record. Label : UMC. Cat Num : 3513884. Barcode : 0602435138848.

Release Date : January 8th 2021

The release of living legend Barry Gibb’s 2021 album ‘Greenfields: The Gibb Brothers Songbook Vol. 1′. The album will include new renditions of some of Bee Gees’ biggest hits, that Barry Gibb has re-recorded with of the world’s biggest country artists – including Dolly Parton, Keith Urban, Olivia Newton-John and Sheryl Crow.
